<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Scrabble Words From Electricity — Valid Electrical Terms</h1>
<p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6">Published June 15, 2026 · 5 min read</p>

<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">The world of electricity is packed with short, high-scoring words perfect for Scrabble. From the 3-letter powerhouse OHM to bingo-worthy VOLTAGE and AMPERAGE, electrical vocabulary gives you access to uncommon letter combinations that most opponents won't challenge.</p>

<h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">Top Scoring Electrical Words</h2>

<div class="not-prose my-6 p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10">
  <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-6 text-center">
    <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">40+</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Valid electrical terms</p></div>
    <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">24 pts</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">QUARTZ (highest)</p></div>
    <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">3–9</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Letter range</p></div>
  </div>
</div>

