    <p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">OHM is your secret weapon:</span> At 8 points for just 3 letters, OHM averages 2.67 points per tile — better than most 5-letter words. Use it to score in tight spaces.</p>
